# Project Skill Context — AI Stock Analytics

> This rule injects project-specific context into **generic skills** at runtime.
> Skills remain universal; this file provides the local overrides.

## Product Identity

| Key | Value |
|-----|-------|
| **Name** | AI Stock Analytics (AI 주식 분석 플랫폼) |
| **Abbreviation** | ASA |
| **Domain** | Financial data analysis · Event studies · Trading strategies |
| **Target Users** | Individual investors, quant traders, financial data analysts |

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 19 · TypeScript 5.9 · Vite 7 · Tailwind CSS 4 · Radix UI · Recharts · TanStack Query/Table |
| Backend | Python 3.12 · FastAPI · SQLAlchemy 2.0 · Alembic · Pydantic v2 |
| Database | PostgreSQL 16 |
| Testing | Vitest (unit) · Playwright (E2E) · pytest (backend) |
| Icons | lucide-react only |

## Design System

This project uses the **Refined Swiss** theme via **Tailwind CSS v4 + Radix UI**.

- Token definitions: `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc`
- CSS variables: `frontend/src/index.css`
- Fonts: Inter (body), Fira Code (numbers/code)
- Dark mode: CSS Custom Properties auto-switch

**Not used in this project:**
- `@thakicloud/shared` (TDS) — do not import or reference
- Figma — no design files; specs are in code and markdown
- Storybook — not configured
- Go backend — Python only
- Kubernetes / Helm / Terraform — not deployed to K8s

## Terminology Rules

When skills produce output for this project:
- Use "AI Stock Analytics" or "ASA", not "AI Platform", "Thaki Cloud", or "ai-platform-webui"
- Use "종목" for stock ticker, "시그널" for trading signal, "스크리닝" for screening
- Use "분석 리포트" for analysis report, "매매 전략" for trading strategy
- Full glossary: `.cursor/skills/references/project-overrides/project-terminology-glossary.md`

